{"tid":678123,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"呢幾個月嚴重失眠 求解決方法","createTime":"2018-05-25T20:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T00:01:59.000Z","uid":172801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c66b279f8ef79f8a6d06098319ffa4ac4f935c12","tid":678123,"uid":172801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T20:17:28.000Z","msg":"呢幾個月 日日一點上床 碌到4.5點先有睡意<br />\n10-11點就醒<br />\n<br />\n大家有無解決方法<br />\n唔想咁快死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"693bebbe1c73a6bd1079a82cbc95547f946b37ca","tid":678123,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T20:32:00.000Z","msg":"捱多5日就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9cb0bae96e318a88aff889ea2c8162dbf7a2e8","tid":678123,"uid":59746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T20:32:24.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都叫失眠？<br />\n純粹你生活習慣問題"},{"pid":"1551efd5fecdc06a30d75bb47c9dbe072c0bc0ac","tid":678123,"uid":125903,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T21:45:16.000Z","msg":"4，5點訓得著就唔叫失眠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f6611cd826578decd49caf7cc23b89ef8dc00c","tid":678123,"uid":89063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T21:49:18.000Z","msg":"真係要強迫自己去瞓（不過真實都係廢話，因為可以你已經試過）<br />\n我記得萬寧屈臣氏有melatonin買，長食就不了，不過食幾日（同時強迫自己去瞓）可以調節番個生理時鐘"},{"pid":"bd4ac930351e5d8330706a5cbeed572920d71850","tid":678123,"uid":89063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T21:53:27.000Z","msg":"不過可能係你噤電話姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上床前30分鐘真係唔好用電子產品啦<br />\n我自己就會用少少set honey沖暖水飲，我覺得飲完個人會舒服啲同好瞓啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eaf59cdb8e63e1fbb9a796fda3a523377b54e51","tid":678123,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T00:01:59.000Z","msg":"你而家生理時鐘亂左。<br />\n勉強一晚唔好訓，<br />\n到夜晚好眼訓時12點前訓著，<br />\n習慣返個時間就會好訓返。"}]}